text: Aneko is a settlement in Kenya's Migori County. == History == Before the Kenyan general election in 2013, Aneko voted as part of the Nyanza Province.initially aneko was small island in nyatike subcounty. it borders two rivers. river kuja to the north and migori to the south and lake victoria to the west. == References == Category:Populated places in Nyanza Province
title: Aneko
